name: Robotics Talks
description:
Greetings, Robotics Enthusiasts!  

Robotics is an expanding industry. There aren't enough programmers with the knowledge to program robots, even though we are aware that the demand for robotics developers is increasing. You now have the opportunity to distinguish yourself from the other engineers in the world. Your edge over other developers will be obvious if you join the robots development bandwagon right now.

We are women in robotics, Delhi preparing for our inaugural event, where roboticists will speak on Introduction to  Robotics and SLAM. Anyone (of any gender) who is interested in learning about robotics is welcome to attend this free session. We'll discuss the potential of robotics as well as the variety of careers available in the field.


Prerequisite Note - No prerequisite is needed.

Please have a look at the details in this email and confirm your RSVP by clicking the link :
https://meetingplace.io/women-in-robotics-delhi/events/9660

Please join the Google meet link below on 9th October 2022 from 7:30 pm - 8:15 pm
http://meet.google.com/nmw-hhus-hym

name: WiR Organizers & Volunteers Get Together
description:
If you're helping Women in Robotics or interested in volunteering then this meeting is for you. 
Let's create more local chapters and events, more online activities, more stories and inspiring content. Bring your ideas, your enthusiasm and your questions.
